# Wisest Maths — Cursor Rules

## Link Performance (<2s target, <800ms ideal)

See full rule: `.cursor/rules/link-performance.mdc`

- Server components: `AppLink` from `@/components/app-link`
- Client components: `FastLink` from `@/components/fast-link`
- Every route segment: `loading.tsx` with `@/components/link-skeletons`
- Solve pages: `loadQuestionWithSiblings` — never `allQuestions` for nav
- Verify: `npm run build && npm run start && npm run perf:links`
